></a>\n<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" class=\"link social_link share-link btn_copy\" title=\"Link\"><img src=\"https://s.vnecdn.net/english/i/v51/graphics/icon-link.svg\" alt=\"Link\"><span class=\"tip\" style=\"display: none; position: relative;top: -60px;background: #17191A;color: #fff !important;white-space: nowrap;\">Copy link</span></a>\n<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" class=\"share_email_article\" title=\"send mail to friend\"><em class=\"fa fa-envelope-o\"></em></a>\n<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" class=\"print print_content\" title=\"Print\"><img src=\"https://s.vnecdn.net/english/i/v51/graphics/print.svg\" alt=\"Print\"></a>\n</div>\n</div>	<div class=\"detail-flex__right\">\n<div class=\"block_breakumb_web\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"folder_name_detail\" data-campaign=\"Header\">\n<a class=\"folder_name_main\" href=\"/news/news\">News</a>\n<a class=\"active\" data-medium=\"Menu-Traffic\" href=\"/news/news/traffic\">Traffic</a>\n<a data-medium=\"Menu-Environment\" href=\"/news/news/environment\">Environment</a>\n<a data-medium=\"Menu-Education\" href=\"/news/news/education\">Education</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h1 class=\"title_post\">100 join HCMC metro\'s first full-line trial run</h1>\n<div class=\"author\">\nBy <a href=\"javascript:void(0)\">Quiynh Tran, Thanh Tung, Gia Minh, Dinh Van</a>&nbsp; &nbspAugust 29, 2023 | 02:47 pm GMT+7 </div>\n<div class=\"lead_news_photo_detail\">\nA maiden test run on the entire line of HCMC’s metro No.1 on Tuesday carried over 100 passengers through all 14 stations, including three underground, between Thu Duc City and District 1. </div>\n<article class=\"content_detail fck_detail width_common\">\n<div id=\"article_content\" class=\"block_ads_connect\">\n<div class=\"item_slide_show clearfix vertical-thumb \">\n<div class=\"block_thumb_slide_show\">\n<img alt=\"100 join HCMC metro\'s first full-line trial run\" data-reference-id=\"33011489\" src=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2023/08/29/metro-JPG_1693284746-1693285053.jpg?w=1200&h=0&q=100&dpr=1&fit=crop&s=EDlBvB6rw4sK1cjepLHqCQ\" data-original=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2023/08/29/metro-JPG_1693284746-1693285053.jpg?w=1200&h=0&q=100&dpr=1&fit=crop&s=EDlBvB6rw4sK1cjepLHqCQ\" class=\"vne_lazy_image\" data-original=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2023/08/29/metro-JPG_1693284746-1693285053.jpg?w=1200&h=0&q=100&dpr=1&fit=crop&s=EDlBvB6rw4sK1cjepLHqCQ\" data-original=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2023/08/29/metro-JPG_1693284746-1693285053.jpg?w=1200&h=0&q=100&dpr=1&fit=crop&s=EDlBvB6rw4sK1cjepLHqCQ\" class=\"vne_lazy_image\" class=\"left displayAfterResize vne_lazy_image\" data-component-caption=\"&amp;lt;div&amp;gt;\n&amp;lt;p class=&amp;quot;Normal&amp;quot;&amp;gt;A train of HCMC\'s metro line No.1 departs Ben Thanh underground station in District 1 at 9:15 a.m.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;\n&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;\n\n&amp;lt;div&amp;gt;\n&amp;lt;p class=&amp;quot;Normal&amp;quot;&amp;gt;The station lies in front of the city’s iconic Ben Thanh Market.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;\n&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;\n\n&amp;lt;div&amp;gt;\n&amp;lt;p class=&amp;quot;Normal&amp;quot;&amp;gt;For the first test run on the entire line, the train took three trips and the trial was completed at 12:30 p.m. One covered the entire 19.7-km line from Ben Thanh Station to Suoi Tien Station opposite the eponymous theme park in Thu Duc City, and the others covered 10 km from Ben Thanh to An Phu in Thu Duc.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;\n&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;\"/>\n<noscript>\n<img class=\"displayAfterResize left\" alt=\"100 join HCMC metro\'s first full-line trial run\" data-reference-id=\"33011489\" src=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2023/08/29/metro-JPG_1693284746-1693285053.jpg?w=1200&h=0&q=100&dpr=1&fit=crop&s=EDlBvB6rw4sK1cjepLHqCQ\" data-original=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2023/08/29/metro-JPG_1693284746-1693285053.jpg?w=1200&h=0&q=100&dpr=1&fit=crop&s=EDlBvB6rw4sK1cjepLHqCQ\" class=\"vne_lazy_image\" data-component-caption=\"&amp;lt;div&amp;gt;\n&amp;lt;p class=&amp;quot;Normal&amp;quot;&amp;gt;A train of HCMC\'s metro line No.1 departs Ben Thanh underground station in District 1 at 9:15 a.m.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;\n&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;\n\n&amp;lt;div&amp;gt;\n&amp;lt;p class=&amp;quot;Normal&amp;quot;&amp;gt;The station lies in front of the city’s iconic Ben Thanh Market.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;\n&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;\n\n&amp;lt;div&amp;gt;\n&amp;lt;p class=&amp;quot;Normal&amp;quot;&amp;gt;For the first test run on the entire line, the train took three trips and the trial was completed at 12:30 p.m. One covered the entire 19.7-km line from Ben Thanh Station to Suoi Tien Station opposite the eponymous theme park in Thu Duc City, and the others covered 10 km from Ben Thanh to An Phu in Thu Duc.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;\n&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;\"/>\n</noscript>\n<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" class=\"icon_thumb_videophoto icon_thumb_zoom btn_icon_show_slide_show\"><i class=\"ic ic-zoom-in\"></i></a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"desc_cation\"><div>\n<p class=\"Normal\">A train of HCMC\'s metro line No.1 departs Ben Thanh underground station in District 1 at 9:15 a.m.</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p class=\"Normal\">The station lies in front of the city’s iconic Ben Thanh Market.</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p class=\"Normal\">For the first test run on the entire line, the train took three trips and the trial was completed at 12:30 p.m. One covered the entire 19.7-km line from Ben Thanh Station to Suoi Tien Station opposite the eponymous theme park in Thu Duc City, and the others covered 10 km from Ben Thanh to An Phu in Thu Duc.</p>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item_slide_show clearfix vertical-thumb \">\n<div class=\"block_thumb_slide_show\">\n<img alt=\"100 join HCMC metro\'s first full-line trial run\" data-reference-id=\"33011490\" src=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2023/08/29/metro-30-JPG-1693285050.jpg?w=1200&h=0&q=100&dpr=1&fit=crop&s=3hdotZWI8Wi54dy5URVi6Q\" data-original=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2023/08/29/metro-30-JPG-1693285050.jp